            {
               "text": "### Images from Tula\n\nThese images are copyright for Tula and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 2</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"img4\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img4', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Representation of a ruler measuring a line. The source code is available on the project’s GitHub (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('240800f3-ede4-4deb-9d4e-915a3a03fa68'); return false;\"><i>History Tracers Team, 05/30/2024</i></a>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 2</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"img3\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img3', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Cylindrical column pieces that overlap. Photo taken on <htdate0>, during a visit to the archaeological site.</div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
