               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "### Image Descriptions\n- **Slide 1 / 2**: Representation of a ruler measuring a line. The source code is available on the project’s GitHub (*History Tracers Team, 05/30/2024*).\n- **Slide 2 / 2**: Cylindrical column pieces that overlap. Photo taken on <htdate0>, during a visit to the archaeological site.",
